Package: UCRBSpatialTools
Title: Quick tools for plotting and converting coordinates and river miles
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
  person("Christopher", "Michaud", , "christioher_michaud@fws.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package contains functions to convert River and river mile to spatial coordinate pairs and Coordinate pairs to River and river mile. Some functions return sf dataframes which can be piped into mapview for rapid mapping while others return maps directly.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
